---

You can also expand all the paths in a model by calling [makerjs.model.expandPaths](/docs/api/modules/makerjs.model.md#expandpaths):

```javascript
//expand a star model
var m = require('makerjs');
var star = m.model.rotate(new m.models.Star(5, 100), 18);
var expanded = m.model.expandPaths(star, 10);
var model = {
models: {
star: star,
outline: expanded
}
};
var svg = m.exporter.toSVG(model);
document.write(svg);
```


